{
  "stem": "10496.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was interested in government.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One year.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just one year.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, New York.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Columbia in one year.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I made it in one year, the Masters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I went to the service for the Korean War.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was between 1953 and '55.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I met my wife during that period.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--we got married.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I was mostly in-- in the-- in the shipping area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, I was shipping soldiers in-- out and in, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Receiving them.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Soldiers that were-- came from all parts of-- all parts of the world.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and I also took care of the finances.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The finances with the-- you know, how much these soldiers were getting, and everything else.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would-- I would process those things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think the-- the reason that I never went overseas, basically, is because I met my wife during that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when we got married--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1954.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- when we came-- when I came back, I had less than a year to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't pay the-- Uncle Sam to-- to-- pay me-- pay them to go over to Korea.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Besides, 1953, a truce was signed anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But no one knew exactly how long that truce was going to last.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lillian.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lillian.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I met her during a-- during a dance in-- in-- in the Fort, in-- in Fort Dix.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was love at first sight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, we just had a proper chemistry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Asbury Park, New Jersey.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, when I-- when I got out, my first job was in Asbury Park, New Jersey.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was the teacher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a teacher, and-- and that's where we lived together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "High school.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "High school.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- they also needed a-- a German teacher, so it worked out nicely.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
